                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6053" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1526</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9199 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上下求索，推陈出新——小米公司新零售转型之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Exploring up and down, innovating through the old —the road of Xiaomi&#39;s new retail transformation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">赵晓铃，曹翠珍，雷雨嫣，杨德义，刘泽甲</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安邮电大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京小米科技有限责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新零售；战略管理；战略分析</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">new retail; strategic management; strategic analysis</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">早期的小米公司依托互联网平台和性价比策略迅速发展壮大，而随着竞争对手的持续涌入，国内电子商务市场趋于饱和，在线平台的客户获取成本持续上升，为谋求进一步发展，小米公司在2016年以小米之家为试点进行新零售探索，采用线上线下同款同价策略，取得良好效果后在全国范围内快速扩张其新零售业务；然而激进的扩张又为接下来一系列新难题的出现埋下了伏笔。2019年小米面对新的战略环境，调整了新零售战略目标和路径规划，结果成效显著。从小米新零售战略的确定、发展以及面对新环境的战略调整，本案例旨在帮助学生理解和掌握企业战略制定和调整的相关理论和方法，深刻认识到企业需要根据自身实力和外部环境适时调整战略发展方向，从而在激烈的市场竞争中胜出。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all"> The early Xiaomi company relied on the Internet platform and cost-effective strategy to develop rapidly. With the continuous influx of competitors, the domestic e-commerce market has become saturated, and the cost of customer acquisition on online platforms has continued to rise. In order to seek further development, Xiaomi company in 2016 In the year, Xiaomi’s home was used as a pilot to explore new retail, using the same online and offline strategy of the same price, and after achieving good results, it rapidly expanded its new retail business nationwide; however, the radical expansion was the next series of new problems. The appearance laid the groundwork. Faced with the new strategic environment in 2019, Xiaomi adjusted its new retail strategic goals and path planning, and the results were remarkable. From the determination and development of Xiaomi&#39;s new retail strategy and the strategic adjustment in the face of the new environment, this case aims to help students understand and master the relevant theories and methods of corporate strategy formulation and adjustment, and deeply realize that companies need to be timely based on their own strength and external environment Adjust the strategic development direction to win in the fierce market competition.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《审计理论与实务》、《管理会计》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略环境分析</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-03</td>
